  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Using an adult lung bench model of non invasive ventilation, the aim of the study is to
      compare an experimental system of breath-synchronized vibrating mesh nebulizer to a
      conventional vibrating mesh nebulizer during non invasive ventilation in terms of inhaled and
      lost doses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
